.S.A &amp; Canadian Region having Experience and In-depth knowledge of Bringing the best of Shipping and Logistics Rates on Continued basis.</p>\r\n<p>Team Agriosa trust that with the continuing hard work, honesty and integrity, we are proudly moving towards to generate revenue in S eight digits annually. Agriosa Canada believes huge potential in Indian market and accordingly Agriosa Impex Private Limited being formed in the year 2016.</p>\r\n<p>Each new business opportunity offers our valuable upgrading experience in servicing its customers and principles with great humility and model efficiency. Agriosa enters the new millennium in a true spirit of mutual growth and inter connections with its valued clients and international associates, indeed, in all thanks giving to the God Almighty.</p>\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n<p>[/kc_column_text][kc_single_image image_size=\"full\" _id=\"938786\" image_source=\"media_library\" image=\"74\"][kc_row_inner _id=\"168776\" cols_gap=\"{`kc-css`:{}}\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`background`:{`background|`:`eyJjb2xvciI6IiNlOGU4ZTgiLCJsaW5lYXJHcmFkaWVudCI6WyIiXSwiaW1hZ2UiOiJub25lIiwicG9zaXRpb24iOiIwJSAwJSIsInNpemUiOiJhdXRvIiwicmVwZWF0IjoicmVwZWF0IiwiYXR0YWNobWVudCI6InNjcm9sbCIsImFkdmFuY2VkIjowfQ==`}}}}\"][kc_column_inner width=\"100%\" _id=\"562242\"][kc_row_inner# column_align=\"middle\" video_mute=\"no\" _id=\"926465\"][kc_column_inner# width=\"50%\" _id=\"47138\"][kc_spacing height=\"97px\" _id=\"667339\"][kc_title text=\"T3VyIFRlYW0=\" _id=\"389811\" type=\"h1\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{}}\"][kc_column_text _id=\"460929\"]</p>\r\n<p>Under the leadership of Mr. K.Bains (Chairman) our team Mr. Joseph Csaba, Ms. Susan Skemp &amp; Mr. Jerrald Jones collectively has international trade experience and accord careful personal attention for every shipment. We have exceptional procedures in place to facilitate efficient movement of all kinds of product to the end user. Our team can directly take care of your specific requirem