`:{`text-align|,p`:`center`},`box`:{`background|`:`eyJjb2xvciI6IiNmZmZmZmYiLCJsaW5lYXJHcmFkaWVudCI6WyIiXSwiaW1hZ2UiOiIlU0lURV9VUkwlL3dwLWNvbnRlbnQvdXBsb2Fkcy8yMDIwLzA3L0Fncmlvc2EtbG9nby0zMDB4MTEyLnBuZyIsInBvc2l0aW9uIjoiMCUgMCUiLCJzaXplIjoiYXV0byIsInJlcGVhdCI6InJlcGVhdCIsImF0dGFjaG1lbnQiOiJzY3JvbGwiLCJhZHZhbmNlZCI6MX0=`,`display|`:`block`}}}}\"]</p>\r\n<p><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n<p><strong>A</strong>griosa is a Canadian Based Company formed by National and International Promoters to cater Global export and import business, and all the promoters\' expertise in Farming, Transport, Shipping, Hospitality, Manufacturing, Construction, Real Estate &amp; Trading in Various Commodities Segments.</p>\r\n<p>They are globally exporting Agro Commodities like Pulses, Oats and Fruits, They specialize to grow Blueberries, Raspberries, cranberries also seasonally produce Strawberries.<strong>A</strong>griosa is a Canadian Based Company formed by National and International Promoters to cater Global export and import business, and all the promoters\' expertise in Farming, Transport, Shipping, Hospitality, Manufacturing, Construction, Real Estate &amp; Trading in Various Commodities Segments.</p>\r\n<p>Agriosa has collaborations in the manufacturing of Wines, Beer &amp; Spirits of Canada, U.S.A, Russia, Ukraine, India &amp; Spain.</p>\r\n<p>Agriosa Globally trades in Metals &amp; minerals more than a decade.</p>\r\n<p>Company Promoters Owns and Associates with various Farms, Farmlands and Pulses Processing Centers at Canada and U.S.A., promoters owns and operates their own Transports having 350 trucks and also associates with the association of 1000 owner operators throughout Canada and U.S.A.</p>\r\n<p>They also own other brands (Pubs, Night Clubs and Motels) throughout Canada and U.S.A.</p>\r\n<p>Our Promoters have very close relations with some of the of the Top Shipping companies like C.G.A and C.M.A, one of the promoter of our company is a Senior Consultant In-charge of U.S.A &amp; Canadian Region having Experience and In-depth knowledge of Bringing the best of Shipping and Logistics Rates on Continued basis.</p>\r\n<p>Team Agriosa trust that with the continuing hard work, honesty and integrity, we are proudly moving towards to generate revenue in S eight digits annually. Agriosa Canada believes huge potential in Indian market and accordingly Agriosa Impex Private Limited being formed in the year 2016.</p>\r\n<p>Each new business opportunity offers our valuable upgrading experience in servicing its customers and principles with great humility and model efficiency. Agriosa enters the new millennium in a true spirit of mutual growth and inter connections with its valued clients and international associates, indeed, in all thanks giving to the God Almighty.</p>\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n<p>[/kc_column_text][kc_single_image image_size=\"full\" _id=\"501330\" image_source=\"media_library\" image=\"74\"][kc_row_inner _id=\"335345\" cols_gap=\"{`kc-css`:{}}\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`background`:{`background|`:`eyJjb2xvciI6IiNlOGU4ZTgiLCJsaW5lYXJHcmFkaWVudCI6WyIiXSwiaW1hZ2UiOiJub25lIiwicG9zaXRpb24iOiIwJSAwJSIsInNpemUiOiJhdXRvIiwicmVwZWF0IjoicmVwZWF0IiwiYXR0YWNobWVudCI6InNjcm9sbCIsImFkdmFuY2VkIjowfQ==`}}}}\"][kc_column_inner width=\"100%\" _id=\"271267\"][kc_row_inner# column_align=\"middle\" video_mute=\"no\" _id=\"266468\"][kc_column_inner# width=\"50%\" _id=\"674292\"][kc_spacing height=\"97px\" _id=\"805834\"][kc_title text=\"T3VyIFRlYW0=\" _id=\"152366\" type=\"h1\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{}}\"][kc_column_text _id=\"475257\"]</p>\r\n<p>Under the leadership of Mr. K.Bains (Chairman) our team Mr. Joseph Csaba, Ms. Susan Skemp &amp; Mr. Jerrald Jones collectively has international trade experience and accord careful personal attention for every shipment. We have exceptional procedures in place to facilitate efficient movement of all kinds of product to the end user. Our team can directly take care of your specific requirements and all necessary export documentation. Our business credo is total honesty and full transparency in everything we handle.</p>\r\n<p>[/kc_column_text][/kc_column_inner#][kc_column_inner# width=\"50%\" _id=\"466922\"][kc_spacing height=\"54px\" _id=\"295265\"][kc_single_image image_size=\"full\" _id=\"263192\" image_source=\"media_library\" image=\"85\"][/kc_column_inner#][/kc_row_inner#][kc_row_inner# column_align=\"middle\" video_mute=\"no\" _id=\"88556\"][kc_column_inner# width=\"50%\" _id=\"737848\"][kc_title text=\"T3VyIE1pc3Npb24=\" _id=\"760540\" type=\"h1\"][kc_column_text _id=\"423102\"]</p>\r\n<p>At Agriosa with thorough research we ensure Superior quality &amp; Product Safety &amp;Value <br />for money to our customers at international and Domestic Markets.</p>\r\n<p>Our Mission is to stand by our commitment and provide on long term sustainability on the best of Quality and product Safety and Value for Money to our Customers that protects the trust of our customers in the Agriosa Brand.</p>\r\n<p>[/kc_column_text][/kc_column_inner#][kc_column_inner# width=\"50%\" _id=\"318803\"][kc_title text=\"T3VyIFZpc2lvbg0K\" _id=\"640588\" type=\"h1\"][kc_column_text _id=\"49620\"]</p>\r\n<p>Our Vision is to create Customer delight by helping our valuable customers around the world to eat healthier &amp; live healthier. Our vision is about meeting consumers\'</p>\r\n<p>needs and making food an easier choice that is healthier &amp; more enjoyable part of life. Our Vision lets everyone well informed right from our employees to customers, Consumers and communities wherever we manufacture and sell our products and what we care about. It not only captures the essence of wellness and health but it also embodies all the ways we can eat and live better such as the safety and value of the products and the services and the solutions we offer.</p>\r\n<p>[/kc_column_text][/kc_column_inner#][/kc_row_inner#][kc_row_inner# column_align=\"middle\" video_mute=\"no\" _id=\"289581\"][kc_column_inner# width=\"100%\" _id=\"282947\"][kc_title text=\"Q29yZSBWYWx1ZXM=\" _id=\"475410\" type=\"h1\"][kc_column_text _id=\"1530\"]</p>\r\n<p><strong>Agriosa</strong> provides a Honest, Transparent and Clean culture at its work premises. We handle our brands ,employees ,customers , consumers,vendors ,suppliers ,communities with utmost care and affection.</p>\r\n<p>[/kc_column_text][/kc_column_inner#][/kc_row_inner#][/kc_column_inner][/kc_row_inner][/kc_column][/kc_row][kc_row use_container=\"yes\" _id=\"847206\"][kc_column width=\"12/12\" video_mute=\"no\" _id=\"83216\"][kc_title text=\"UnVubmluZyBQcm9qZWN0cw==\" _id=\"137470\" type=\"h1\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`title-style`:{`text-align|+.kc_title,.kc_title,.kc_title a.kc_title_link`:`center`}}}}\"][kc_column_text _id=\"39056\"]</p>\r\n<div style=\"mso-element: frame; mso-element-frame-width: 520.0pt; mso-element-frame-height: 35.2pt; mso-element-wrap: auto; mso-element-anchor-vertical: page; mso-element-anchor-horizontal: page; mso-element-left: 37.75pt; mso-element-top: 73.25pt;\">\r\n<table width=\"693\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"padding: 0cm;\" align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" height=\"70\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 17.5pt; background: white; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',sans-serif; color: white; background: black; mso-shading: black; mso-pattern: solid black;\">Agriosa &amp; promoters has the exclusive online distribution rights for all products of <br /><span style=\"letter-spacing: -.05pt;\">Patanjali Ayurved Limited through one of its associate </span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"http://www.shudhbuy.com/\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',sans-serif; color: blue; letter-spacing: -.05pt; background: black; ms