 Canadian Region having Experience and In-depth knowledge of Bringing the best of Shipping and Logistics Rates on Continued basis.</p>\r\n<p>Team Agriosa trust that with the continuing hard work, honesty and integrity, we are proudly moving towards to generate revenue in S eight digits annually. Agriosa Canada believes huge potential in Indian market and accordingly Agriosa Impex Private Limited being formed in the year 2016.</p>\r\n<p>Each new business opportunity offers our valuable upgrading experience in servicing its customers and principles with great humility and model efficiency. Agriosa enters the new millennium in a true spirit of mutual growth and inter connections with its valued clients and international associates, indeed, in all thanks giving to the God Almighty.</p>\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n[/kc_column_text][kc_row_inner _id=\"607400\" cols_gap=\"{`kc-css`:{}}\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`typography`:{`overflow|`:`overlay`},`background`:{`background|`:`eyJjb2xvciI6InRyYW5zcGFyZW50IiwibGluZWFyR3JhZGllbnQiOlsiIl0sImltYWdlIjoiJVNJVEVfVVJMJS93cC1jb250ZW50L3VwbG9hZHMvMjAyMC8wNy9waWMtMzAweDEzNy5qcGciLCJwb3NpdGlvbiI6ImNlbnRlciBjZW50ZXIiLCJzaXplIjoiY29udGFpbiIsInJlcGVhdCI6Im5vLXJlcGVhdCIsImF0dGFjaG1lbnQiOiJmaXhlZCIsImFkdmFuY2VkIjoxfQ==`},`box`:{`display|`:`flex`}}}}\"][kc_column_inner width=\"100%\" _id=\"862136\"][kc_spacing height=\"500px\" _id=\"306488\"][/kc_column_inner][/kc_row_inner][kc_row_inner _id=\"191866\" cols_gap=\"{`kc-css`:{}}\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`background`:{`background|`:`eyJjb2xvciI6IiNlOGU4ZTgiLCJsaW5lYXJHcmFkaWVudCI6WyIiXSwiaW1hZ2UiOiIlU0lURV9VUkwlL3dwLWNvbnRlbnQvdXBsb2Fkcy8yMDIwLzA3L3NoYXBlX2JyaWdodF9ncmVlbl9wYWxlXzcyNDBfMTkyMHgxMDgwLmpwZyIsInBvc2l0aW9uIjoiMCUgMCUiLCJzaXplIjoiYXV0byIsInJlcGVhdCI6InJlcGVhdCIsImF0dGFjaG1lbnQiOiJzY3JvbGwiLCJhZHZhbmNlZCI6MX0=`}}}}\"][kc_column_inner width=\"100%\" _id=\"548425\"][kc_row_inner# column_align=\"middle\" video_mute=\"no\" _id=\"698697\"][kc_column_inner# width=\"50